Hunt.Name: Full Hunting Grounds
Hunt.Message: Four or five Yellows against one  Green.  The object is for Green to stay alive for six minutes.  That's not so hard... is it?

HtSm.Name: Small Hunting Grounds
HtSm.Message: Specially optimized for smaller games.  Two to five Yellow against one or two Green.  The object is for Green to stay alive for three minutes.  That's not so hard... is it?

BlHt.Name: Ball Hunting
BlHt.Message: Two to five Yellow try to protect the goal from one Green.  You have six minutes.  Play nice!

MnFd.Name: Minefield
MnFd.Message: Two to Five Yellow against one Green.  The object is for Green to stay alive for three minutes.  That's not so hard... is it?  Oh yea, green has another weapon or two to use...

TGHT.Name: The Great Hunt
TGHT.Message: Yellow tries to hunt down green in this jungle setting.  Two to five Yellow against one Green. The object is for Green to stay alive for four minutes.

Duck.Name: Fish in a Barrel
Duck.Message: Two to five Yellow try to protect their wounded HECTOR from one or two Green.  You have three minutes.

Chkb.Name: ChokeBox
Chkb.Message: This is NOT a hunting level.Layout similiar to the infamous Choke.  But not QUITE the same.

DefB.Name: D-Ball
DefB.Message: This is NOT a hunting level.Yellow vs. Green ballgame.  Yellow tries to defend their goal from Green.  You have four minutes.  Play nice!
